channel.title: Some of my Minecraft builds
channel.description:
Well I love minecraft, I have played a server called Ntfwc's free map server for about 3 weeks now and here is some of the stuff I have built.
NOTE : The images are 8-9mb total. Also I am hosting them off my website so it is another increase in image size.
Well this is a building I created last night, the car I created a couple of weeks ago, there are more buildings behind the huge one (university campus) and if you want a picture of them too just ask ;)
[img]http://www.artyarts.com/BigBuilds.png[/img]
Well this is my main map, it has stuff like a toy box, teddy bear, bed, desk, cinema, control booth, storage rooms and even food!
[img]http://www.artyarts.com/HiSkiller.png[/img]
[img]http://www.artyarts.com/HiSkiller2.png[/img]
The next 2 houses are a group of 10 I will be making ;)
[img]http://www.artyarts.com/Loghouse.png[/img]
[img]http://www.artyarts.com/ModernHouse.png[/img]
This was a project that has not been finished yet, and no the buildings aren't just plain squares.
[img]http://www.artyarts.com/City.png[/img]
Thanks guys.
